HEADWORD: Saturnicentric
<hw>Sat`urn*i*cen"tric</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<fld>(Astron.)</fld> <def>Appearing as if seen from the center of the
planet Saturn; relating or referred to Saturn as a center.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Saturnine</ent>⟦br⟧
